      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 epitomizes reliable luxury. The Eminent White Pearl exterior retains a deep gloss, complemented by a pristine Parchment leather interior that shows only the slightest signs of careful use on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, having followed every scheduled maintenance interval at the dealership\u2014full service records are available for your review. It comes equipped with the Premium Package, featuring a power moonroof, heated and ventilated front seats, and a heated wood-trimmed steering wheel. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently serviced. It has been consistently garage-kept by a non-smoker, ensuring a fresh, odor-free cabin environment. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway driving, the overall presentation is sharp and professional. This is a turnkey SUV ready for its next owner to enjoy years of refined performance and comfort.",
